---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - ModernCMS">
	<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="text-center">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
				About ModernCMS
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
				Learn about our mission to revolutionize content management
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-16">
			<div class="prose prose-primary mx-auto">
				<h2>Our Mission</h2>
				<p>
					ModernCMS was born from a simple idea: content management should be simple, fast, and enjoyable. We believe that creating and managing content shouldn't require a computer science degree or hours of training.
				</p>

				<h2>Built for the Modern Web</h2>
				<p>
					Unlike traditional CMS platforms that were built for a different era of the internet, ModernCMS is designed from the ground up for today's web. We leverage modern technologies and best practices to deliver a lightning-fast, secure, and scalable platform.
				</p>

				<h2>Features that Matter</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Modern block editor for intuitive content creation</li>
					<li>Real-time collaboration tools</li>
					<li>Built-in SEO optimization</li>
					<li>Responsive design preview</li>
					<li>Advanced media management</li>
					<li>Robust security features</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Open Source</h2>
				<p>
					We believe in the power of community. ModernCMS is open source, meaning anyone can contribute to making it better. Our growing community of developers and content creators helps shape the future of the platform.
				</p>

				<h2>Get Started Today</h2>
				<p>
					Ready to experience a better way to manage content? <a href="/register" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">Sign up for free</a> and join thousands of content creators who have already made the switch to ModernCMS.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>